{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "17", "m": "11", "Y": "2025"}, "time": {"H": "10", "M": "12", "S": "10"}}, "news": [{"title": "Pune: RMC units seek more time to comply with MPCB\u2019s new guidelines", "para": "Ready-mix concrete manufacturers and real estate developers in Pune have requested an extension to comply with new Maharashtra Pollution Control Board (MPCB) guidelines. The regulations mandate canopy coverings for RMC units to control dust, but industry stakeholders cited procedural issues and the need for coordination with the Pune Municipal Corporation for permissions before building these structures.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/cement/pune-rmc-units-request-deadline-extension-for-mpcb-compliance/125381075?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-195135/125381075.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "cement"}, {"title": "Goa: 'Settlement' zone land in ODPs, regional plan to get zoning certificates from TCP", "para": "Goa's TCP department will now issue zoning certificates for land converted under Calangute-Candolim and Arpora-Nagoa-Parra ODPs, provided it's designated as 'Settlement' in Regional Plan 2021. This follows a Supreme Court decision upholding a High Court ruling that set aside the ODPs, emphasizing the need to prevent Goa from becoming a 'concrete jungle'.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/goas-tcp-department-to-issue-zoning-certificates-for-settlement-land-in-controversial-odps/125381209?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-244928/125381209.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Kalyan-Dombivli civic body launches one-window online portal system to prevent illegal constructions", "para": "In response to illegal constructions, Kalyan-Dombivli Municipal Corporation has launched KD SWIFT, Maharashtra's first one-window online system for building permissions. This digital platform streamlines approvals from eight departments within a 28-day deadline, ensuring transparency and preventing malpractice. Citizens can now track applications and receive QR-coded certificates for instant verification, fostering trust and curbing future irregularities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/technology/kalyan-dombivli-launches-kd-swift-a-game-changer-in-building-permissions/125381141?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-68262/125381141.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "technology"}]}